# Design guidelines pack

- **Start:** `design-guidelines/OVERVIEW.md` (summary, tokens, components).
- **Reuse in other repos:** copy the whole `design-guidelines/` folder; read `design-guidelines/README.md`.
- **Granular rules:** `design-guidelines/rules/**/*.mdc` (buttons, tables, sidebar, layout, …).

Engineering policy and refactors still live under `.ai/core/`. Product module framing: `.ai/projects/merchant-dashboard.md`.
